cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.SE 

This paper proposes a secure and privacy-preserving mix service for bitcoin anonymity, which involves cryptography and security (cs.CR), as well as distributed systems and databases (cs.DC, cs.DB). The paper also discusses the scalability and accountability of the proposed solution, which relates to computer networks (cs.SE) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
